latestPosts.caption:
I can’t believe that in just a few months, you’ll be miles away from me. The thought of waking up and not having you beside me, not hearing your voice first thing in the morning, honestly haunts me. You’ve always been my constant, my guide, my safe place. Being your younger sister, I’ve looked up to you my whole life — your strength, your love, your laugh — and now everything’s changing.

With your wedding coming closer, all the excitement is mixed with this ache in my heart. I’m so proud of you and happy for everything ahead, but I can’t help feeling emotional. You’re not just my sister; you’re my best friend, my second mom, and my biggest cheerleader. Life without your daily presence will be so different. But no matter where you are, you’ll always carry a piece of my heart with you.

Just don’t forget — no matter the distance, I’m always here, loving you endlessly.🫂❤️

@bhoomikagehani2806
